Text:
Please help me get my first torrent right out their and shared, and please seed this for as long as possible, I have it sitting in Vuze permantly seeding for anyone wanting this fantastic game, If this torrent takes off, I will upload Jets 'n' Guns - Gold Edition, which is another fantastic scrolling shooter, except this time its a side scrolling shooter with a massive array of weapon combination and upgrades, highly addictive game!

Also, an complete ISO of Memory Wurfel, another fantastic game!

Jets n Guns Gold Screenshots: http://www.google.com.au/search?q=jets+n+guns+gold&biw=1920&bih=976&tbm=isch&tbo=u&source=univ&sa=X&ei=l9yzUYLFMdGXiQful4D4Cw&ved=0CDsQsAQ

Memory Wurfel is a tiles/block game, in gorgouse 3D, where you have to match up 2 suiting blocks with the identicle face, difficulty ranges from easy to hardcore, with every aspect of the game fully customizable!

Hardwood Solitaire III & IV
The best solitaire game ever created on the PC, with the most gorgouse graphics ever seen in any game of its genre, with full customization, and 100+ diffirent game types, check out the demo's here: http://www.google.com.au/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=hardwood%20solitaire&source=web&cd=1&cad=rja&ved=0CCoQFjAA&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.silvercrk.com%2Fsolitaire%2F&ei=vt2zUfW6MM2viQe8sICIDA&usg=AFQjCNEL0PZYDp4WP7OOXrs-fnuLchjmig&bvm=bv.47534661,d.aGc
